 general election|2004]]\n|[[Ganesh Prasad Singh]]\n|[[Rashtriya Janata Dal]]\n|-\n|[[2009 Indian general election|2009]]\n|[[Jagdish Sharma]]\n|[[Janata Dal (United)]]\n|-\n|[[2014 Indian general election|2014]]\n|[[Arun Kumar (Bihar politician)|Arun Kumar]]\n|[[Rashtriya Lok Samata Party]]\n|-\n|[[2019 Indian general election|2019]]\n|[[Chandeshwar Prasad]]\n|[[Janata Dal (United)]]\n|}\n\n==Election results==\n{{Election box begin | title=[[2019 Indian general elections]]: [[Jehanabad|Jahanabad]]}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link||party=Janata Dal (United)|candidate=Chandeshwar Prasad Chandravanshi|votes=3,35,584|percentage=42.17}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link||party=Rashtriya Janata Dal|candidate=Surendra Yadav|votes=3,33,833|percentage=41.95}}\n\n{{Election box candidate with party link||party=Rashtriya Samata Party (Secular)|candidate=Dr [[Arun Kumar (Bihar politician)|Arun Kumar]]|votes=34,558|percentage=4.34}}\n\n{{Election box candidate with party link||party=None of the above|candidate=[[None of the Above]]|votes=27,683|percentage=3.48}}\n{{Election box majority||votes=1,751|percentage=0.22|change     = }}\n{{Election box turnout||votes=8,22,233|percentage=51.76|change     = }}\n{{Election box gain with party link|\n   |winner     =Janata Dal (United)\n   |loser      =Rashtriya Lok Samata Party\n   |swing      =\n }}\n{{Election box end}}\n{{Election box begin | title=[[2014 Indian general elections]]: [[Jehanabad|Jahanabad]] <ref>{{cite web| url = http://eci.nic.in/eci_main/archiveofge2014/33%20-%20Constituency%20wise%20detailed%20result.pdf | title=General Election of India 2014, Constituencywise detail result|publisher=Election Commission of India |accessdate=2015-09-23 |page=80}}</ref><ref name=web-arch-turnout>{{cite web|title=Parliamentary Constituency wise Turnout for General Election - 2014 |url=http://eci.nic.in/eci_main1/GE2014/PC_WISE_TURNOUT.htm |publisher=ECI New Delhi |accessdate=2015-09-23 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=